sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant W as Web App
    participant P as Payment API
    participant E as Email Service

    U->>W: Click "Pay now"
    W->>P: Create payment intent
    P-->>W: Intent created
    W->>P: Confirm payment
    alt Payment approved
        P-->>W: Success
        W->>E: Send receipt email
        E-->>U: Receipt delivered
        W-->>U: Show confirmation page
    else Payment failed
        P-->>W: Declined
        W-->>U: Show retry options
    end
